RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

95-108. Armco, Inc. v. N. Assur. Co. of Am. Butler County, No. CA94-02-026.

Reported at 72 Ohio St.3d 1407, 642 N.E.2d 495, and 72 Ohio St.3d 1533, 650 N.E.2d 110. It is ORDERED by the court that the motion for reconsideration of this court’s dismissal for want of prosecution be, and is hereby, denied, effective June 8, 1995.
